{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-types-post-js","path":"/2008/07/08/christie-trailer/","result":{"data":{"page":{"title":"Christie Comedy Series Trailer  (3 min)","uri":"/2008/07/08/christie-trailer/","content":"\n<center><div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;display:inline-block;\"><iframe src=\"https://flowplayer.com/e/?t=CHRISTIE%20FILMAKA%20SERIES&amp;%2FZmlsbV9pZD0yMDY2IiwianMiOltdLCJjc3MiOltdfQ%3D%3D&amp;r=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.filmaka.com%2Fchriste-series.php%3Ffilm_id%3D2066\" allowfullscreen=\"\" style=\"border:none;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;\"></iframe><div style=\"padding-top:56.25%;\"></div></div></center>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>In 2008 my brother entered an online film making competition and I helped out. We didn&#8217;t win, but we had a bloody good laugh making a series of comedy videos for the web.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>The trailer video I made along with <a href=\"https://www.filmaka.com/christe-series.php?film_id=2066\">the whole comedy series can be found on Fimaka.com</a></strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<!--more-->\n\n\n\n<p>I edited <a href=\"https://www.filmaka.com/christe-series.php?film_id=2066\">this trailer for the &#8216;Christie&#8217; internet comedy series</a> using Final Cut Pro.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The trick for making the trailer was to write TV guide descriptions of each episode and from those establish the common story for the series and base it on that: &#8220;Mo, a toilet salesman, is slowly driven mad by Christie, his incompetent boss.&#8221;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>I think it stands up pretty well against the professional trailer<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IKJaoCMzAcc\"> that Filmaka later commissioned</a> from a proper production house (maybe better?)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The series was commissioned by Bend It Like Beckham producer Deepak Nayar and the former head of Fox Entertainment Sandy Grushow after the director won a <a href=\"http://www.filmaka.com/\">filmaka.com</a><a href=\"http://www.filmaka.com/filmaka_christie.php\">.</a> short film competition.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The series was shot low budget with a minimal crew so I did a variety of jobs in production, post-production and new media. Besides making the trailer I worked as a production assistant on set, made the behind the scenes documentary, worked on the bloopers &amp; out-takes video and I make a couple of heavily disguised cameo appearances.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>I also worked on a wryly internet marketing campaign including making the web page, writing e-mail newsletters and &#8216;pimping up&#8217; a <a href=\"http://www.myspace.com/lavulike\"><s>MySpace page</s></a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can watch the full Christie series on <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IKJaoCMzAcc&amp;feature=PlayList&amp;p=8F5EC9D6A8848FD9&amp;index=0&amp;playnext=1\">YouTube</a>, <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/pages/Christie/15991448677\">facebook</a>, and with additional extras at <a href=\"https://www.filmaka.com/christe-series.php?film_id=2066\">filmaka.com</a><a href=\"http://www.filmaka.com/filmaka_christie.php\">.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can find more up-to-date videos and links <a href=\"http://www.alecchristie.com/performer\">on my brother Alec Christie&#8217;s web site</a>&nbsp;and <a href=\"https://comedy.louiechristie.com\">my comedy website</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Footnotes</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The tune in the trailer is <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/2XvklQlrQQwRBbu1IxNi3r?si=AXN9Ro-hQXiXYXBRwMfdng\">Lover Killer</a> by <a href=\"http://www.thefoxesband.co.uk/\">The Foxes.</a></p>\n","date":"July 8, 2008","excerpt":"<p>In 2008 my brother entered an online film making competition and I helped out. We didn&#8217;t win, but we had a bloody good laugh making a series of comedy videos for the web. The trailer video I made along with the whole comedy series can be found on Fimaka.com. I edited this trailer for the [&hellip;]</p>\n","featuredImage":{"node":{"altText":"","localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#080808","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/blog/static/4feb9dbb7f4b2d8d7e6d064ecbea257a/9595a/christie-and-mongo.jpg","srcSet":"/blog/static/4feb9dbb7f4b2d8d7e6d064ecbea257a/db353/christie-and-mongo.jpg 151w,\n/blog/static/4feb9dbb7f4b2d8d7e6d064ecbea257a/69850/christie-and-mongo.jpg 302w,\n/blog/static/4feb9dbb7f4b2d8d7e6d064ecbea257a/9595a/christie-and-mongo.jpg 604w","sizes":"(min-width: 604px) 604px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/blog/static/4feb9dbb7f4b2d8d7e6d064ecbea257a/3a27a/christie-and-mongo.webp 151w,\n/blog/static/4feb9dbb7f4b2d8d7e6d064ecbea257a/fd503/christie-and-mongo.webp 302w,\n/blog/static/4feb9dbb7f4b2d8d7e6d064ecbea257a/e86db/christie-and-mongo.webp 604w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 604px) 604px, 100vw"}]},"width":604,"height":413}},"publicURL":"/blog/static/4feb9dbb7f4b2d8d7e6d064ecbea257a/christie-and-mongo.jpg"},"mediaDetails":{"width":604,"height":413}}},"author":{"node":{"name":"Louie Christie","firstName":"Louie","lastName":"Christie","uri":"/author/louiechristie/","description":"Adventurous, tech geek, available to hire, underground comedian in my own head. ðŸ˜¬","avatar":{"url":"http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/f4961bd6f78e6ebb70c62064997391de?s=96&d=mm&r=g","width":96,"height":96,"imageFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/blog/static/ffd32b248d79a5230defa7cee1460b01/f2806/f4961bd6f78e6ebb70c62064997391de.jpg","srcSet":"/blog/static/ffd32b248d79a5230defa7cee1460b01/f2806/f4961bd6f78e6ebb70c62064997391de.jpg 80w","sizes":"80px"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/blog/static/ffd32b248d79a5230defa7cee1460b01/99ff4/f4961bd6f78e6ebb70c62064997391de.webp 80w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"80px"}]},"width":80,"height":80}}}}}},"categories":{"nodes":[{"name":"Trailer","slug":"trailer","uri":"/category/trailer/"}]}},"nextPage":{"title":"Possibly The Worlds Most User Friendly DVD Menu","uri":"/2008/07/20/possibly-the-worlds-mos